Feature: Empty Cart Checkout Prevention  Scenario: Proceed to Checkout button should be disabled when cart is empty    Given I am on the cart page    And there are no items in the cart    Then the 'Proceed to Checkout' button should be disabled  Scenario: Proceed to Checkout button should be enabled when cart has items    Given I am on the cart page    And there are items in the cart    Then the 'Proceed to Checkout' button should be enabled